# ─── macOS Code Signing & Notarization ───
# Required for distributing the app without Gatekeeper warnings.
#
# 1. APPLE_ID          — Your Apple ID email (the one registered with Apple Developer Program)
# 2. APPLE_APP_SPECIFIC_PASSWORD — An app-specific password generated at https://appleid.apple.com/account/manage
# 3. APPLE_TEAM_ID     — Your 10-character Apple Developer Team ID (visible at https://developer.apple.com/account)
# 4. APPLE_IDENTITY    — (Optional) Signing identity name. Defaults to "Developer ID Application".
#                         Run `security find-identity -v -p codesigning` to list available identities.
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values. NEVER commit .env to version control.

APPLE_ID=
APPLE_APP_SPECIFIC_PASSWORD=
APPLE_TEAM_ID=
# APPLE_IDENTITY=Developer ID Application: Your Name (TEAMID)
